Ninja Juicer
The Ninja Juicer combines the chemical augmentation of the standard Juicer
with martial arts training and a philosophy of discipline. Where ordinary
Juicers fight with reckless fury, Ninja Juicers apply their enhanced reflexes
and strength with controlled precision.

Ninja Juicers choose from Physical, Weapons, Espionage, and Military skill
categories. They train extensively in melee and ranged combat and are among
the fastest, most dangerous hand-to-hand fighters in the Rifts world.

Note: Like all Juicers, Ninja Juicers carry the weight of their augmentation's
life expectancy. The chemicals that make them extraordinary will eventually
kill them.

Attribute requirements: IQ 9, ME 10, PS 11, PP 12.
Starting equipment: Environmental body armor, vibro-sword, one ranged weapon
of choice, and a small credit reserve.
